articles.title: Coco Gauff, Iga Swiatek cruise into US Open third round - ESPN - ESPN
articles.description: American star Coco Gauff advanced to the third round of the US Open with a straight-sets win Wednesday, as did top seed and defending champion Iga Swiatek.
articles.content:
Aug 30, 2023, 02:46 PM ET
NEW YORK -- Coco Gauff cruised into the third round of the US Open on Wednesday with a 6-3, 6-2 victory over Russian teenager Mirra Andreeva.
